---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
import BackgroundSection from '../components/BackgroundSection.astro'
---

<Layout title="Behind the Scenes | Brianna Marie Rickey">
  <main>
    <BackgroundSection
      backgroundImage="/backgrounds/bts-background.jpg"
      opacity={0.6}
      textOutline={true}
    >
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Behind the Scenes</h1>

      <p class="text-lg mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        This portfolio wasn’t just built—it was carefully crafted with intention, iteration, and a
        whole lot of trial and error.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-10">Elevator Pitch</h2>
      <p class="max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">
        This is a fully responsive cybersecurity portfolio website built in VSCode using Astro,
        React, and Tailwind CSS. It showcases my skills and projects through an intuitive design
        with dynamic views and easy navigation optimized for both mobile and desktop. The site
        focuses on clean, maintainable code, leveraging AI tools to speed up development while
        ensuring I deeply understand and control every part of the project.
      </p>

      <section class="overflow-x-auto mt-12">
        <table class="min-w-full border border-gray-300 text-left text-sm text-gray-800">
          <thead class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 font-semibold">
            <tr>
              <th class="border px-4 py-2">Phase</th>
              <th class="border px-4 py-2">Key Actions & Decisions</th>
              <th class="border px-4 py-2">Outcome</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td class="border px-4 py-2">1. Project Bootstrapping</td>
              <td class="border px-4 py-2"
                >Create Astro project, minimal cleanup, remove `README.md`, init Git</td
              >
              <td class="border px-4 py-2">Clear Astro skeleton structure</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border px-4 py-2">2. Core Styling</td>
              <td class="border px-4 py-2"
                >Install Tailwind, update `tailwind.config.cjs`, `postcss.config.cjs`, global styles
                in `src/styles/global.css`</td
              >
              <td class="border px-4 py-2">Tailwind utilities available project-wide</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border px-4 py-2">3. React Integration</td>
              <td class="border px-4 py-2">Install React, `@astrojs/react`</td>
              <td class="border px-4 py-2">Ready to drop in JSX components</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border px-4 py-2">4. Netlify Adapter</td>
              <td class="border px-4 py-2"
                >Install `@astrojs/netlify`, set config in `astro.config.mjs`, add adapter to
                `import`</td
              >
              <td class="border px-4 py-2">Auto builds use Netlify-friendly output</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border px-4 py-2">5. Global Layout</td>
              <td class="border px-4 py-2"
                >Created `src/layouts/Layout.astro` with shared header/footer</td
              >
              <td class="border px-4 py-2">Single shared shell for every page</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border px-4 py-2">6. Pages</td>
              <td class="border px-4 py-2">Home, About, Projects, Behind the Scenes</td>
              <td class="border px-4 py-2">Clear, minimal routing</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border px-4 py-2">7. Components</td>
              <td class="border px-4 py-2"
                >Made `BackgroundSection.astro`, `ProjectCard.astro`, etc.</td
              >
              <td class="border px-4 py-2">Re-usable chunks per section</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border px-4 py-2">8. PDFs & Static Assets</td>
              <td class="border px-4 py-2"
                >Placed all PDFs in `public/projects/` and linked in cards</td
              >
              <td class="border px-4 py-2">Downloads open in new tab</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border px-4 py-2">9. Git & GitHub</td>
              <td class="border px-4 py-2">Commits, `.gitignore`, pushed to GitHub</td>
              <td class="border px-4 py-2">Source fully tracked & visible</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border px-4 py-2">10. Netlify Deployment</td>
              <td class="border px-4 py-2">Connected repo → Netlify → auto-deploy from `main`</td>
              <td class="border px-4 py-2">Live site with deploy preview</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border px-4 py-2">11. Post-Launch Polish</td>
              <td class="border px-4 py-2"
                >Added `redirects` file, final `astro.config.mjs` cleanup</td
              >
              <td class="border px-4 py-2">Production-ready polish</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </section>

      <div class="text-center mt-12">
        <a
          href="/"
          class="inline-block bg-blue-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded hover:bg-blue-700 transition"
        >
          Back to Home
        </a>
      </div>
    </BackgroundSection>
  </main>
</Layout>
